options.text: Oh sorry, I hadn't realised it was private.
I'm bigger than you. Let me by!

bcf3b435-f1d5-45ce-9024-a4b578997fa5.title: <title>
bcf3b435-f1d5-45ce-9024-a4b578997fa5.text:
This is the home of the Mountain Dwarves. How would
you like it if I wanted to take a short cut through your
home?

options.text: Ooh... is this a short cut to somewhere?
Oh sorry, I hadn't realised it was private.
If you were my friend I wouldn't mind it.

160a8e81-92e1-4f59-a9b5-5272c848c7fb.title: <player>
160a8e81-92e1-4f59-a9b5-5272c848c7fb.text: Ooh... is this a short cut to somewhere?

3b1e3345-126e-4aa3-8dbc-a3c3f2989034.title: <title>
3b1e3345-126e-4aa3-8dbc-a3c3f2989034.text:
Well, it is a lot easier to go this way to get past White
Wolf Mountain than through those wolf filled passes.

options.text: I was wondering what was down those stairs?
I was just stopping to say hello!

b4105734-cdc6-473e-908c-c09e31790208.title: <player>
b4105734-cdc6-473e-908c-c09e31790208.text: Oh, sorry, I hadn't realised it was private.

bd94401d-095c-4a9c-bc85-2ed1c5001067.title: <player>
bd94401d-095c-4a9c-bc85-2ed1c5001067.text: I'm bigger than you. Let me by!

683f4fef-ff73-49fd-b71f-7aeef39ed5ef.title: <title>
683f4fef-ff73-49fd-b71f-7aeef39ed5ef.text: Go away! You're not going to bully your way in", "HERE!

73245357-589e-4e06-83cc-76a55f853258.title: <player>
73245357-589e-4e06-83cc-76a55f853258.text: If you were my friend I wouldn't mind.

22be8613-def7-4766-bf79-4e5f8a9a7c35.title: <title>
22be8613-def7-4766-bf79-4e5f8a9a7c35.text: Yes, but I don't even know you.

options.text: You're a grumpy little man aren't you?

a2263afd-d21b-4f67-bcdd-b695bed82b18.title: <player>
a2263afd-d21b-4f67-bcdd-b695bed82b18.text: You're a grumpy little man aren't you?

073ea82c-63ad-4b95-a66e-bdd58324ac3f.title: <title>
073ea82c-63ad-4b95-a66e-bdd58324ac3f.text:
I don't make friends easily. People need to earn my
trust first.

options.text: And how am I meant to do that?
You're a grumpy little man aren't you?

43556f98-7835-49aa-895f-d0b334a00fd0.title: <player>
43556f98-7835-49aa-895f-d0b334a00fd0.text: And how am I meant to do that?

2cbed5cf-4d11-4731-b31d-ba02a4ce32e0.title: <title>
2cbed5cf-4d11-4731-b31d-ba02a4ce32e0.text: My, we are the persistent one aren't we?

7b9094ea-e5f6-461f-9df1-7fcc3b6cff90.title: <title>
7b9094ea-e5f6-461f-9df1-7fcc3b6cff90.text:
Well, there's a certain gold artefact we're after. We
dwarves are big fans of gold! This artefact is the first
prize at the Hemenster fishing competition.

076821e3-d2ba-4b9e-a0ae-9f1eb9f931f7.title: <title>
076821e3-d2ba-4b9e-a0ae-9f1eb9f931f7.text:
Fortunately we have acquired a pass to enter that
competition...

3c293a1f-6a64-4d3b-9806-4d8d3794e53e.title: <title>
3c293a1f-6a64-4d3b-9806-4d8d3794e53e.text: Unfortunately Dwarves don't make good fishermen.

2b7878da-d6f1-42be-b583-0d2b1f34c1ed.title: <title>
2b7878da-d6f1-42be-b583-0d2b1f34c1ed.text:
Okay. I entrust you with our competition pass. Don't
forget to take some gold with you for the entrance fee.

aedeee97-12ac-4980-903d-f535fb2a4a82.text: You got the Fishing Contest Pass!

145b457b-db96-4048-bba5-24cd4c43f851.title: <title>
145b457b-db96-4048-bba5-24cd4c43f851.text: Go to Hemenster and do us proud!

63921816-71ea-423b-bf34-8cdba663ef93.title: <player>
63921816-71ea-423b-bf34-8cdba663ef93.text: I was just wondering what was down those stairs?

options.text: I'm bigger than you. Let me by.

46f2aa5c-29b5-47fa-95f6-324a3bdcc582.title: <title>
46f2aa5c-29b5-47fa-95f6-324a3bdcc582.text: Because you can't. So that's fine.

038f5a0b-2489-4452-a485-0dd46de606bd.title: <player>
038f5a0b-2489-4452-a485-0dd46de606bd.text: I was just stopping to say hello!

0d401716-7b10-47a7-9ee3-756915628cb3.title: <title>
0d401716-7b10-47a7-9ee3-756915628cb3.text: What if I do! It's no business of yours.

571b520f-74c1-4bfa-aeaf-d567cd1ecff8.title: <title>
571b520f-74c1-4bfa-aeaf-d567cd1ecff8.text:
Well don't give up! Maybe old Jack can give you a few
tips.

77bc4a13-29e9-4726-b8d9-7b74d6a69496.title: <title>
77bc4a13-29e9-4726-b8d9-7b74d6a69496.text: You'd better go win it then hadn't you?

267fb081-bd45-4ba9-837c-c192a23c55f2.title: <title>
267fb081-bd45-4ba9-837c-c192a23c55f2.text:
Well done! That's brilliant! Do you have the trophy with
you?

194251e4-89e4-4d7e-a4ef-735e6e1c1c68.title: <player>
194251e4-89e4-4d7e-a4ef-735e6e1c1c68.text: Uh... I don't have it with me.

77323e0f-48ee-449b-a6cb-46163a9ecc04.title: <title>
77323e0f-48ee-449b-a6cb-46163a9ecc04.text: You'd better go get it then hadn't you?

f45921e6-6ade-4127-804c-8ac2da64581f.title: <player>
f45921e6-6ade-4127-804c-8ac2da64581f.text: Yep, I have it right here!

488c8490-1338-46d8-a3c2-d9d5bf7c53cd.title: <title>
488c8490-1338-46d8-a3c2-d9d5bf7c53cd.text:
Oh! It's even more shiny and gold than I thought
possible...

4bef7b23-b612-41ea-b848-e489fa64f586.title: <title>
4bef7b23-b612-41ea-b848-e489fa64f586.text:
You've done us proud. Thank you. I think we can
now trust you enough to let you in...

87e54fd7-a239-4edd-96f9-c0125cc34c6f.title: <title>
87e54fd7-a239-4edd-96f9-c0125cc34c6f.text:
Why the tunnel of course! You may now come and go
freely, avoiding the wolves and dangers of the cold, high
mountain. You could even stop in for a beer or two!

70d356a5-dfc5-415f-b4be-d13e615d9fe2.title: <player>
70d356a5-dfc5-415f-b4be-d13e615d9fe2.text: Excellent. That will come in most handy.

84fb4792-5abb-4009-8635-410fab69d012.title: <title>
84fb4792-5abb-4009-8635-410fab69d012.text:
Welcome, oh great Fishing Champion! Feel free to pop by
and use our tunnel any time.

c0068896-20ae-411d-96b1-c88069b5ac81.title: <player>
c0068896-20ae-411d-96b1-c88069b5ac81.text: Thank you, I think I'll stop by for a beer one day.
